{"tid":1468673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦: 因時制宜","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:17:26.000Z","uid":60386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e88d4f4f027f30b193e87a38afbdd5c8d580b253","tid":1468673,"uid":60386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:51:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=2238b194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n唔好亂！！！！！！！<br />\n唔好自亂陣腳！！！！<br />\n好灰 好頹 唔知點做 唔知點行落去<br />\n用少少時間聽返天琦曾經講過嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n：條條大路通羅馬<br />\n邊一個方式可以推翻政府，就去做<br />\n你相信邊個方式，就去做<br />\n唔好因為其他人批評你就放棄<br />\n亦唔好盲目相信自己嘅道路<br />\n而反對其他人嘅做法<br />\n因時制宜<br />\n革命唔會一時三刻成功<br />\n但係又可能突然一時三刻成功<br />\n革命其實係五年前已經靜悄悄開始左<br />\n夢想係實現之前都係好似痴人說夢話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明前嘅黑暗係至撚黑暗呀！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n呢兩個月大家做左幾多犧牲左幾多<br />\n先行到呢一步！<br />\n革命<br />\n會流血<br />\n會失敗<br />\n會有犧牲<br />\n如果政府冇令你犧牲<br />\n代表你對政府冇威脅<br />\n我地宜家對佢地構成威脅<br />\n準備鬥爭 準備奪權<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一個由下而上嘅革命<br />\n人民唔應該害怕政府，政府應該害怕人民</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割席<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\nHONGKONGERS ASSEMBLE</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAC0kTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAC0kTm.png&h=c9502593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcr0Tn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcr0Tn.png&h=220d1d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d2f896687689e0945f2926357376a359bb1bc09","tid":1468673,"uid":60386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:52:21.000Z","msg":"自推！！！！"},{"pid":"04eb43fc084797590ca153ba8711f8929cebc42a","tid":1468673,"uid":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推 就算冇嘢輸都唔可以輸"}]}